{"tid":2026940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公平咩？持摺櫈追打途人稱自衞　建築工獲判","createTime":"2020-05-21T09:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T09:07:01.000Z","uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c52e75dc72a25e91788225ad045545b4fff66e89","tid":2026940,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EcD8bJraE1OqmtdOGiHSkA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/4b5179b7d5b0628f1464f2f8aec72826\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FEcD8bJraE1OqmtdOGiHSkA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F4b5179b7d5b0628f1464f2f8aec72826&h=4f40c38e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=dc44025c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】去年9月15日炮台山及北角一帶，有多宗涉及「福建幫」追打市民及記者的暴力事件，其中一名穿白衣、持摺櫈進入炮台山港鐵站追打市民的地盤工，早前承認一項管有攻擊性武器並有所意圖罪，今日（21日）在東區法院被判接受240小時社會服務令。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n裁判官判刑時指本案案情嚴重，途人若見到48歲被告李河龍手持摺櫈會感到驚慌，惟法庭亦接納被告是因為自衞才持摺櫈上街，加上他在認罪後已被還押兩周，相信已收阻嚇作用，故決定接納感化官建議判處被告接受社會服務令。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n辯方求情指，被告已感到後悔，承認犯案時沒有想清楚法律後果。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n案情指，事發當晚8時，有持不同政見人士在英皇道及炮台山站打鬥，被告被發現手持摺櫈襲擊多人，警方一度將他截停但抄下其身份證資料後便放行。其後翻看現場錄影片段，發現他事發時一直持摺櫈沿英皇道追打途人，更曾進入炮台山港鐵站內用摺櫈襲擊其他人，遂將他拘捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf3e8c90aba10d65aefa2375e10cd778b94c819","tid":2026940,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6122cba953542849759552192e0ae16f1b8887","tid":2026940,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:04:54.000Z","msg":"求幫推<br />\n[香港文化] 上連登打正字<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2026832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2026832</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cbea86a523ce01b9ade783471bafe14f15cdc1a8","tid":2026940,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f0b945da4c4a351fd2efff9e9136e2e365f022","tid":2026940,"uid":173179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"拎住張摺凳自衛"}]}